# Open-Synth License Information

The Open-Synth project by Glyxon Biolabs is committed to Open Science and Decentralized Biotechnology.

## 1. Hardware & Bio-Designs: CERN-OHL-S v2
All hardware schematics (EWOD cartridge designs), genetic construct maps (TdT-Car9), and laboratory protocols in this repository are licensed under the **CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Strongly Reciprocal (CERN-OHL-S)**.

Link: https://ohwr.org/project/cernohl/wikis/Documents/CERN-OHL-version-2

